Specific Objectives
By the end of this topic, the
learner should be able to:
a) identify and describe types
of sculpture
b) identify and describe the
elements and principles of
Art and Design in sculpture
c) select and describe
appropriate materials and
tools for modeling, carving
and construction
d) use appropriate materials
tools, equipment and
techniques in the execution
of a sculpture of functional
and aesthetic function
e) use skills of presentation to
enhance the final
appearance of the sculptures
produced.
